=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44860fda6c68316ee4be88634ad2fb9e00b039f","tid":586693,"uid":175721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T22:07:10.000Z","msg":"屌身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完snapchat無覆 去到凌晨sd左個snap黎 岩先起身滿心歡喜諗住打開 點撚知係一張相黎然後話sd錯 真心心都碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363e901f4e1d342b6caaa6c60e668610a4c5974b","tid":586693,"uid":175721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T22:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢都係玩我炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都有叫我傻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>對呢啲男仔要打心理戰 唔可以搵咁密亦唔可以覆得咁快</blockquote>依家搵親佢都係hea覆 廢事搵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明以前都係佢搵我 唉</blockquote>之前借左佢野 仲要還返比佢 點解我咁命苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌我都借左野比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次見到佢都會忍唔住笑得好燦爛 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f32623aa2ccdce8c6a25d5c705994dad6ff5ba6","tid":586693,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T22:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你靚唔靚女先？</blockquote>普通樣 但關事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好好奇點解你會覺得唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe63576120790945d26d0861e1e25b20034e2f1a","tid":586693,"uid":60517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T23:22:34.000Z","msg":"搵你攝時間<br />\n如果真係想人地對你有興趣<br />\n應該學返佢 得閒先一兩句<br />\n吊返佢轉頭 被佢感受下咩滋味"},{"pid":"9700b1c37c1cd8cfd51cfba402e64a19cc8